                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6020" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0912</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8185 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">何以“纸包火”而不是“水灭火”：华锐风电连续9年盈余操纵之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Why not put out fire by water but paper : Continuous earnings manipulation of Sinovel Wind Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雷倩华，李晶晶，余银漩</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华南理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华锐风电科技（集团）股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">能源工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">27 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">连续盈余操纵；战略决策；公司治理；股权结构</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Continuous earnings manipulation, Strategic decision-making, Corporate governance, Ownership structure</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华锐风电股份有限公司在成立初期由于政策利好和管理层的正确决策得到迅速的发展。上市后，风电产业竞争逐渐加剧，产能过剩，政策风向改变，整个行业进入寒冬期，这给刚刚上市的华锐风电带来巨大的打击。应对无措使华锐风电迅速衰败，就此走上连续盈余操纵的道路。上市首年，公司上下合谋，以虚构交易等形式进行财务造假，粉饰报表。一年后，造假之事败露，华锐风电遭到证监会的严惩。当华锐风电连续两年净利润为负，触发退市条款时，其采取了出售应收款、少提预计负债等方式进行盈余管理，实现账面盈利。又连亏两年后，华锐风电故伎重演，通过盈余操纵的方式扭亏为盈，侥幸保“壳”。但是，华锐风电还是在上市九年后遭到市值退市。不注重产品的研发创新与质量更新、不进行根本性的战略变革（“水灭火”），而是多次采用盈余操纵的手段（“纸包火”）进行利润修饰终究没能“救活”华锐。此外，华锐风电的盈余之路与公司股权结构的不合理和公司治理的缺陷和有直接的关系。华锐风电股权分散，大股东只关心自己的收益，缺乏监督的动力。同时，公司内部控制权过于集中，决策缺乏制衡与科学性，造成形势变化时公司应对失误，最终导致公司误入歧途，积重难返。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Due to favorable policies and correct decisions of the management, Sinovel Wind Power Co., Ltd. achieved rapid development in the early stage of its establishment. After the listing, the competition in the wind power industry intensified, and with overcapacity and the change of policy direction,the whole industry entered the cold winter period, which brought a huge blow to Sinovel. Inadequate response led to the rapid decline of Sinovel Wind Power, and thus embarked on the road of continuous earnings manipulation. In its first year as a listed company, the company conspired to fabricate its financial statements in the form of fictitious transactions. One year later, the fraud was exposed and Sinovel was severely punished by the China Securities Regulatory Commission. When the net profit of Sinovel was negative for two consecutive years and the delisting clause was triggered, it carried out earnings manipulation by selling receivables and reducing expected liabilities, so as to realize book profit. After two consecutive years of losses, Sinovel repeated the same trick, that is, through the way of earnings manipulation to turn a loss into a profit, narrowly saved &quot;shell&quot;. Still, Sinovel was delisted nine years after going public. What can save the company is a fundamental strategic change (&quot; put out fire by water &quot;), that requires product R&amp;D innovation and quality renewal, rather than profit decoration by means of earnings manipulation (&quot; put out fire by paper &quot;) . In addition, Sinovel&#39;s earnings path is directly related to the unreasonable ownership structure of the company and the defects of corporate governance. Sinovel&#39;s shareholding is scattered, and the major shareholders only care about their own earnings, and lack the motivation to supervise. At the same time, the internal control of the company is too centralized, and the decision-making is lack of checks and balances and scientific, resulting in the company&#39;s mistakes when the situation changes, and eventually lead to the company to go astray, which is difficult to return.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》、《审计学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">盈余操纵</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-02</td>
                            </tr>
